290
00:16:04,760 --> 00:16:06,680
 Probably not.

291
00:16:06,680 --> 00:16:09,240
 She just really wanted to be second that day.

292
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:13,620
 What drove her to it, I have no idea.

293
00:16:14,620 --> 00:16:19,620
 But then I examined myself, why had I reacted this way?

294
00:16:19,620 --> 00:16:22,900
 The woman didn't know it,

295
00:16:22,900 --> 00:16:25,720
 but her actions attacked my identity.

296
00:16:25,720 --> 00:16:30,600
 Instead of me realizing that her actions said nothing

297
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:33,700
