300
00:16:41,060 --> 00:16:44,340
 Put up for adoption, unwanted,

301
00:16:44,340 --> 00:16:47,700
 not valuable enough to be kept.

302
00:16:47,700 --> 00:16:52,360
 In that moment at the bus line, I was proving myself,

303
00:16:52,360 --> 00:16:57,280
 showing that I was good enough to be in second place,

304
00:16:57,280 --> 00:17:00,820
 shouting loudly inside, "I am valuable."

305
00:17:00,820 --> 00:17:04,540
 In that moment, my actions denied

306
00:17:04,540 --> 00:17:07,340
 everything God has spoken over my life.

