00:17:16,800 --> 00:17:24,100
 He's already shown me who I truly am in his eyes.

310
00:17:24,100 --> 00:17:29,380
 I sinned against that woman that day.

311
00:17:29,380 --> 00:17:31,840
 I didn't love her as myself.

312
00:17:31,840 --> 00:17:35,020
 I placed myself above her,

313
00:17:35,020 --> 00:17:37,440
 and in my thoughts, I judged her.

