00:28:51,740 --> 00:28:54,980
 Caleb had a different spirit.

491
00:28:54,980 --> 00:28:58,060
 He was following God fully.

492
00:28:59,340 --> 00:29:01,860
 Too many of us have been following

493
00:29:01,860 --> 00:29:04,700
